## Feature Overview

This feature adds complete chat logging functionality to the **Anonymous Question Asking Platform**, ensuring that **all chat data is stored in MongoDB** using a **clean and hierarchical structure** based on date, teacher, and room ID.

## Data Storage Structure

The chat data is organized in the following nested MongoDB document format:

```json
{
  "date": {
    "teacher": {
      "room": [
        {
          "sender": "student/teacher",
          "message": "Chat message here...",
          "timestamp": "2025-06-30T10:45:00Z"
        },
      ]
    }
  }
}
```
